created_at.description: The timestamp when the webhook was created

enabled.description: Indicates if the webhook is currently enabled

form_id.description: The unique identifier of the form associated with the webhook

id.description: The unique identifier of the webhook

tag.description: A tag to categorize or label the webhook

updated_at.description: The timestamp when the webhook was last updated

url.description: The URL where the webhook data is sent

verify_ssl.description: Indicates whether SSL verification is enforced for the webhook URL
